cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV. 

The paper discusses a natural language processing task of sentence simplification using neural machine translation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also mentions the use of neural networks, which suggests the possibility of it belonging to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Learning). The use of memory augmented neural networks indicates the possibility of it belonging to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper mentions the use of automatic evaluation measures and human judgments, which suggests the possibility of it belonging to cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
